review.review_text: This was a first time visit and I completely loved it! I ordered the Vermont Chicken with a side of fruit and a cannoli for dessert. I canno...
Grilled tuna is good. Grilled tuna sandwich is good hang over food. Comes with fries. The service is decent. Go early or you could waste you...
Frozen Yogurt. Don't bother getting the frozen yogurt...it's horrible!
PRETTY GOOD FOOD. I pretty much like every sandwich in this restaurant if I tell them to hold the cranberry. That clam chowder is excellent ...
